                  "type": "markdown",
                  "title": "Theme Info",
                  "content": "### Arctic Night Theme\n\n**Card-mod Styles Showcased:**\n- Climate state colors (heat, cool, dry, fan_only, heat_cool, auto)\n- Vacuum state colors (cleaning, returning, paused, error)\n- Generic on-state colors for lights, switches, fans\n- Person border colors (home / not_home)\n- Card header font styling\n\n**GitHub:** [arctic-night-theme](https://github.com/manospasj/home-assistant-arctic-night-theme)"
                }
              ]
